{"sample_id": "2782116", "input": "BPD is pretty much /r/CPTSD. There's research saying that it's a chemically caused dysregulation of emotion from methylation of the body because you're trapped in chronic stress which leads to depression and anxiety.When I was at my worst, I was literally not in control as I was so confused and disoriented. I was a vessel for a tangled webs of extremely heightened emotions that I couldn't cope with, and everything was hair-trigger. My behaviour gradually became more and more extreme because I felt like I needed more validation (I never ever had any) and in doing that, my behaviour was increasingly normalised to me and I didn't realise the extent or impact of my behaviour until now, in hindsight.Talking to people who told me that there was something wrong with me was extremely triggering and sent me plunging into a spiral of self hatred and a loss of hope because I didn't know what was wrong with me at that time./u/onethecamden", "ground_truth_ocean": {"O": -0.1, "C": 0.84, "E": 0.08, "A": 0.24, "N": -0.82}, "detected_ocean": {"O": 0, "C": 0, "E": 1, "A": 0.6000000000000001, "N": 0.15}, "coaching_mode": "policy_navigation", "detector_status": "heuristic", "detector_error": "No valid JSON across benchmark variants", "stage_timings": [{"stage": "detection", "status": "fallback", "duration_ms": 2779}, {"stage": "routing", "status": "ok", "duration_ms": 0}, {"stage": "retrieval", "status": "ok", "duration_ms": 0}, {"stage": "generation", "status": "ok", "duration_ms": 6428}, {"stage": "grounding", "status": "ok", "duration_ms": 0}, {"stage": "verification", "status": "ok", "duration_ms": 0}, {"stage": "end_to_end", "status": "ok", "duration_ms": 9316}], "error": null, "status_code": 200}
